(July 21st, 2016)
This CUSTODIAN AGREEMENT, dated as of July 20, 2016, is made between ALLY FINANCIAL INC., a Delaware corporation, as custodian (Ally Financial or the Custodian), and CAPITAL AUTO RECEIVABLES LLC, a Delaware limited liability company, as depositor (the Depositor).



