ADMINISTRATION AGREEMENT, dated as of July 20, 2016, among CAPITAL AUTO RECEIVABLES ASSET TRUST 2016-2, a Delaware statutory trust, as issuer (the Issuing Entity), ALLY FINANCIAL INC. (Ally Financial), a Delaware corporation, as administrator (the Administrator), and DEUTSCHE BANK TRUST COMPANY AMERICAS, a New York banking corporation, not in its individual capacity but solely as indenture trustee (the Indenture Trustee).



